metadata.name: Elden Dragon 1
metadata.description:
Years ago, before the ass of humanity appeared. There was a world inhabited by mysterious, enormous, wonderful, insane, incredible creatures. The leader of this world was Elden Dragon. Elden Dragon was so terrible and powerful that all the other predators who saw it fled in fear. Unfortunately all Elden Dragons are dead (maybe a few are hiding somewhere). We are here to make you live the legend of Elden Drago.

1,200 unique Elden Dragon collection
